/**
 * Homepage — layout cribbed from the Mivora reference, copy adapted to
 * Ocean Geosynthetics, colors swapped to the live site's brand blue +
 * orange palette. Sections (top to bottom):
 *
 *   1. Hero — full-bleed image, copy overlay, stats card
 *   2. Mission intro — eyebrow + big heading + 3 image cards
 *   3. Industries strip — title + 4 industry cards
 *   4. Services (dark section) — 3 service cards on dark blue
 *   5. Why us — 2 bullet boxes + supporting image, CTA
 *   6. Stats strip — 4 numbers
 *   7. Testimonials — 4 client quote cards
 *   8. CTA banner — image bg, centered call to action
 *
 * Each section reuses the same brand tokens defined in
 * src/styles/variables.css and exposed to Tailwind via @theme.
